data.description: Beautiful unit!!  Welcome to your new home in Chicago's Irving Park neighborhood. This stunning two-bedroom, two-bath timber loft offers the perfect blend of urban living and modern comfort. As you step inside, you'll be immediately captivated by the spaciousness of the unit, featuring soaring 11-foot ceilings that give the space an airy and open feel. This unit has a  private balcony, in unit laundry, indoor heated parking, and plenty of storage. The building itself offers access to a common roof top  and workout room. This secure elevator building is ideally located just steps away from shopping, dining, public transportation, and more! (*Assessments breakdown $285 + $118 for cable & internet.)
